<paragraph blockId="5.[151,609,151,178]" box="[151,609,151,178]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,609,151,178]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" reason="1">
<taxonomicName authority="C. L. Koch, 1836" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[151,609,151,178]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="graeca">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,609,151,178]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,391,151,178]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">Scolopendra graeca</emphasis>
C. L. Koch, 1836
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1405,223,358]" box="[151,384,223,249]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">Original description:</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="130" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1405,223,358]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">
<taxonomicName authority="C. L. Koch 1836" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[197,621,259,286]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="graeca">
<emphasis box="[197,424,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">Scolopendra graeca</emphasis>
C. L. Koch 1836
</taxonomicName>
[1. Oct.]. Text 9.1 [
<emphasis box="[847,976,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">Anmerkung</emphasis>
2, 
<specimenCount box="[1012,1056,259,286]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" type="generic">1 p.</specimenCount>
, unpaginated] - In: Koch, C.L. (1836a) Deutschlands Crustaceen, Myriapoden und Arachniden. Ein Beitrag zur deutschen Fauna. Herausgegeben von Dr. Herrich-Schäffer. [see 
<taxonomicName authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[641,761,331,357]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="clavipes">
<emphasis box="[641,761,331,357]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">S. clavipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
above] 9 
<emphasis box="[865,952,331,357]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">tes Heft</emphasis>
. Regensburg: Fr. Pustet.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,403,753]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">
This case is similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[449,569,403,429]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="clavipes">
<emphasis box="[449,569,403,429]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">S. clavipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see above). The pretended original description in 
<bibRefCitation author="Koch, C. L. &amp; Kritische Revision der Insectenfaune Deutschlands von Dr" box="[1138,1280,403,429]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" pagination="1 - 190" refId="ref6685" refString="Koch, C. L. (1847) Kritische Revision der Insectenfaune Deutschlands von Dr. Panzer and Dr. Herrich-Schaffer, Heft 1 - 190. III. Bandchen, enthaltend die Verzeichnisse und Berichtigungen zu Deutschlands Crustaceen, Myriapoden und Arachniden und ein System der Myriapoden von C. L. Koch [additional title page: System der Myriapoden mit den Verzeichnissen und Berichtigungen zu Deutschlands Crustaceen, Myriapoden und Arachniden. Heft 1 - 40. von C. L. Koch)]. Pustet, Regensburg, 272 pp., 10 pls. [date on title page: 1847, date of preface: 1 April 1846, in the text referred to as &quot; System der Myriapoda &quot;] https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 49866" type="book chapter" year="1847">Koch (1847)</bibRefCitation>
is just a comprehensive redescription from 
<bibRefCitation author="Koch, C. L." box="[498,648,439,465]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" pagination="1 - 90" refId="ref6503" refString="Koch, C. L. (1836 a) Deutschlands Insecten, herausgegeben von G. W. F. Panzer, fortgesetzt von Dr. G. A. W. Herrich-Schaffer. 142. Heft. In: Herrich-Schaffer, G. A. W. (Ed.), Favnae insectorvm Germanicae initia, oder, Deutschlands Insecten, F. Pustet, Nurnberg, pp. 1 - 90. [Author of text and illustrations; the series referred to in the present text as &quot; Herrich-Schaffer series &quot;; published 1 October] https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 15007" type="journal article" year="1836">Koch (1836a</bibRefCitation>
, b). The original description was published as “ 
<emphasis box="[1192,1321,439,465]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">Anmerkung</emphasis>
2” in line with the description of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1837" box="[417,519,475,501]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="italica">
<emphasis box="[417,519,475,501]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">S. italica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<emphasis box="[558,606,475,501]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">Heft</emphasis>
9 of the Koch series and, concurrently, 
<emphasis box="[1065,1113,475,501]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">Heft</emphasis>
142 of the Herrich-Schäffer series without being listed in the index and neither illustrated.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,403,753]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">
The name 
<taxonomicName authority="C. L. Koch, 1836" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1836" box="[315,616,547,574]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="graeca">
<emphasis box="[315,420,547,573]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">S. graeca</emphasis>
C. L. Koch, 1836
</taxonomicName>
is corrected herewith from the wrong “1847” or referenced work “System der 
<taxonomicName box="[195,323,583,609]" class="Myriapoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="135" rank="class">Myriapoda</taxonomicName>
”, respectively (
<bibRefCitation author="Koch, C. L. &amp; Kritische Revision der Insectenfaune Deutschlands von Dr" box="[496,625,583,609]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" pagination="1 - 190" refId="ref6685" refString="Koch, C. L. (1847) Kritische Revision der Insectenfaune Deutschlands von Dr. Panzer and Dr. Herrich-Schaffer, Heft 1 - 190. III. Bandchen, enthaltend die Verzeichnisse und Berichtigungen zu Deutschlands Crustaceen, Myriapoden und Arachniden und ein System der Myriapoden von C. L. Koch [additional title page: System der Myriapoden mit den Verzeichnissen und Berichtigungen zu Deutschlands Crustaceen, Myriapoden und Arachniden. Heft 1 - 40. von C. L. Koch)]. Pustet, Regensburg, 272 pp., 10 pls. [date on title page: 1847, date of preface: 1 April 1846, in the text referred to as &quot; System der Myriapoda &quot;] https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 49866" type="book chapter" year="1847">Koch 1847</bibRefCitation>
, pp. 161, 269, plate 5 detail drawings). The latter reference was used in the sense of the first description e.g. by 
<bibRefCitation author="Koch, C. L." box="[593,818,619,646]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" refId="ref6877" refString="Koch, C. L. (1863 b) Die Myriapoden: getreu nach der Natur abgebildet und beschrieben. Band 2. H. W. Schmidt, Regensburg, 112 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 10639" type="book" year="1863">Koch (1863b pp. 70</bibRefCitation>
, 71, plate 95 habitus), 
<bibRefCitation author="Kraepelin, K." box="[1069,1253,619,645]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" pagination="1 - 276" refId="ref7003" refString="Kraepelin, K. (1903) Revision der Scolopendriden. Mitteilungen aus dem Naturhistorischen Museum in Hamburg, 20 (2), 1 - 276." type="journal article" year="1903">Kraepelin (1903</bibRefCitation>
, p. 254), 
<bibRefCitation author="Attems, C. G." pageId="5" pageNumber="130" pagination="2" refId="ref6130" refString="Attems, C. G. (1930) Myriopoda. 2. Scolopendromorpha. In: Schulze, F. E. &amp; Kukenthal, W. (Eds.), Das Tierreich. Vol. 54. Walter de Gruyter &amp; Co., Berlin and Leipzig, pp. 1 - 308." type="book chapter" year="1930">Attems (1930</bibRefCitation>
, p. 28) and Bonato 
<emphasis box="[438,494,655,681]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">et al.</emphasis>
(2016).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,403,753]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">
The currently accepted name is 
<taxonomicName authority="Latreille, 1829" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1829" box="[572,1007,691,717]" class="Chilopoda" family="Scolopendridae" genus="Scolopendra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scolopendromorpha" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cingulata">
<emphasis box="[572,829,691,717]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">Scolopendra cingulata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Latreille, M." box="[839,1007,691,717]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" pagination="326 - 339" refId="ref7031" refString="Latreille, M. (1829) Les Myriapodes. In: Cuvier, P. M. L., Le regne animal distribue d'apres son organisation. Nouvelle Edition, Revue et Augmentee. Tome IV. Crustaces, Arachnides et Partie des Insectes. Deterville, Paris, pp. 326 - 339." type="book chapter" year="1829">Latreille, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(see Bonato 
<emphasis box="[1164,1223,691,717]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="130">et al.</emphasis>
2016, founded on 
<bibRefCitation author="Kraepelin, K." box="[151,329,727,753]" pageId="5" pageNumber="130" pagination="1 - 276" refId="ref7003" refString="Kraepelin, K. (1903) Revision der Scolopendriden. Mitteilungen aus dem Naturhistorischen Museum in Hamburg, 20 (2), 1 - 276." type="journal article" year="1903">Kraepelin 1903</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
